cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about medical image segmentation using deep learning algorithms, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a strategy for active learning, which involves selecting informative slices for annotation, and this falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper uses attention mechanisms to improve segmentation accuracy, which is a common technique in multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
